# Implementation Plan: Project Hephaestus Core Engine

## Goal
Transform the "Hephaestus Quartet" governance protocols into executable Python logic within [axion-core](file:///c:/Users/Chris/Synarche_Workspace/axion-core). This will enable Axion to autonomously scan, simulate, teach, and optimize.

## Architecture
We will create a new package `axion_core.hephaestus` with the following modules:

```text
axion_core/
└── src/
    └── hephaestus/
        ├── __init__.py
        ├── sentinel.py       # AOP-SENTINEL-SCAN-001 (Autonomous Audit)
        ├── gaze.py           # AOP-ARCH-GAZE-001 (Impact Simulation)
        ├── mentor.py         # UMB-DIDACTIC-001 (Didactic Generator)
        └── soul.py           # METRIC-AES-001 (Elegance Metric)
```

